title: Skyline Views! Dart Access! W/D Incl! Private Yards
posting_body: ['Apartment Homes offers convenience right outside your front door!', 'Hop on the DART at the Medical District or jump in the car for a short drive to Downtown Dallas and some of the best in dining, nightlife, sports, art and entertainment.', 'Everything you want or need is right in your neighborhood.', ' Modern studio, one and two bedroom homes with unique and stylized community spaces.', 'We are convenient to it all.', 'Take in the urban downtown Dallas skyline or enjoy the relaxing wooded area with spring-fed creek.', 'Explore all that Dallas has to offer with convenient access to the best of entertainment, dining and shopping.', 'Some of the Great Amenities that our community offers:', 'Freezer-top stainless refrigerator with ice maker', 'Side-by-side refrigerator with exterior filtered water and ice dispenser', 'Over-the-stove coordinating microwave', 'Modern wood cabinetry with oversized satin nickel pulls', 'Subway tile backsplash', 'Granite countertops with undermount sink', 'Pub height Islands', 'Pendant lights finished in brushed steel with opal glass cover', 'Transitional track lighting in brushed nickel', 'Hardwood style flooring', 'Pantries', 'High-efficiency top-load washer and dryer', 'Walk-in closets', 'Modern brushed steel ceiling fans', 'Private yards', 'Patio french doors and oversized windows', 'Dual, wrap, and fresh air Juliette balconies', 'Creek, urban, and downtown Dallas views', 'Additional storage rooms', 'Garden tub with ceramic tile surround', 'Walk-in showers', 'Granite vanity top with subway tile backsplash', 'Single and double sink vanities with drawers', 'Hardwood style flooring', 'Linen closet', 'And Much More!!', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Apartment Locators', 'show contact info', 'mention Ad 536']
